results.deck: A former sub-division of Mirrorsoft, Arena Entertainment was aquired by Acclaim in 1991 who used the name tp publish games for SEGA console systems (Master System, Game Gear, Genesis & SEGA CD). The brand name ceased to be used in 1995.
